content: Dear Mr. Phillips,Thank you for contacting Capital Metro regarding your request for reimbursement.If you have not activated the pass we may submit your request to our finance department for consideration for reimbursement.Please advise as to what type of pass you have.Once again, thank you for taking the time to contact us and thank you for riding Capital Metro. Please feel free to contact us in the future if you have any concerns, questions or suggestions regarding our service. You may reach ourCustomer Service Department at 512-474-1200 or via our web site atwww.capmetro.org.Thank you,John Torres
